These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, pilot, lawyer, dressmaker
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, argentine, italian
1. the italian is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the manager is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
4. the argentine is on the left or right of the italian##3
5. the manager is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Job   | manager | pilot | dressmaker | lawyer |
| Nationality        | mexican | chinese   | italian | argentine    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, apricot, blood-red, coral
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, collecting, dancing
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who likes black##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Color   | blood-red | black  | apricot  | coral |
| Hobby   | dancing    | filmmaking | collecting | puzzles    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, marigold, poppy
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, mauve, emerald, azure
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
2. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | poppy | marigold | iris    | lily      |
| Color   | emerald        | azure     | purple | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, ship
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend, baccarat, siglo
1. the person driving the snowmobile is between the old-henry-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Transport         | ship | quad-bike | snowmobile | taxi |
| Cigar   | baccarat       | old-henry   | blend    | siglo  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
City: new-york, miami, edinburgh, rome
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, skateboard, helicopter
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| City   | miami  | new-york    | edinburgh   | rome       |
| Transport   | bike | helicopter | skateboard | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, kiwi, spinach, raspberry
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester, siglo, dannemann
1. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | spinach      | kiwi | raspberry | papaya |
| Cigar   | dannemann | ritmeester     | blend  | siglo  |

