.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, alhambra, prince, tiparillo
4 different games are played: whist, poker, chess, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the person playing billiard is the cain-smoker##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | cain | tiparillo | prince | alhambra    |
| Game     | billiard | chess  | whist     | poker |

