.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
House: cape-cod, cottage, colonial, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, trike, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
2. the modern house is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the modern house##3
4. the modern house is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the cape-cod house is between the modern house and the cottage house##2
6. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the taxi is between the cape-cod house and the person driving the trike##2
8. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| House   | cottage | cape-cod      | modern | colonial |
| Transport   | bike  | ship | taxi    | trike            |

