.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, thai, german
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, may, october
1. the thai is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
2. the malaysian is on the right of the russian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in december and the thai##2
4. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
5. the thai is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | german | russian   | malaysian | thai |
| Birthday    | october     | december | april     | may  |

