.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, vegafina, cain, swisher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, december, may
1. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in november and the cain-smoker##2
4. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar      | vegafina       | cain   | dannemann | swisher |
| Birthday   | december | august | may        | november    |

