.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, techno, metal, gospel
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, pineapple, gospel-polo
1. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating gospel-polo##1
4. the person eating gospel-polo is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | gospel   | techno      | metal      |
| Food      | garlic | pineapple | gospel-polo | avocado |

