.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, police-officer, pilot, bartender
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, water, mirinda
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
3. the police-officer is in an even position##4
4. the coach is on the far right##1
5. the pilot is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job          | bartender | police-officer  | pilot  | coach |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | water | 7up | iced-tea   |

