.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, trike, helicopter
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, 7up
1. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Transport   | trike | helicopter | jet-ski | tram |
| Beverage           | 7up     | soy-milk     | milk   | almond-milk         |

