.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, bike, motorbike
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, security-guard, dancer, software-developer
1. the person driving the van is between the entrepreneur and the person driving the airplane##2
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the software-developer is in an odd position##4
6. the dancer is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Transport   | motorbike | airplane         | van   | bike |
| Job   | dancer    | security-guard | software-developer | entrepreneur   |

