.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, cola, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, indie, trance, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is the person drinking cola##1
2. the fan of trance is the person drinking juice##1
3. the fan of indie is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice | cola    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | trance  | jazz | indie     |

