.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, daffodil, tulip
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, carrot, cauliflower, pineapple
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
5. the person eating carrot is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating cauliflower##2
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Flower         | tulip   | daffodil | lily | bellflower    |
| Food   | cauliflower | carrot  | pineapple     | grapefruit |

