.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball-polo, handball, lacrosse, volleyball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, zinnia, bellflower
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball-polo##1
6. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
7. the person who growslily is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Sport   | volleyball | volleyball-polo    | lacrosse       | handball |
| Flower       | begonia  | zinnia | bellflower | lily  |

