3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | january | december | march  | july |
| Flower     | marigold      | dahlia       | aconite | azalea     |

