.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, townhouse, craftsman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball, water-polo, skiing
1. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the futuristic house and the person who's sport is sailing##2
4. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| House         | futuristic | townhouse   | craftsman | gothic-revival |
| Sport   | skiing          | volleyball | sailing         | water-polo  |

 